name: Tooth Fairy box personalized
description:
Let us make you the cutest tooth fairy box ever.

 These are great for tiny keepsakes, ring boxes, but the cutest thing for a little one to put their tooth under their pillow in.

These are adorable for baby shower gifts and can be personalized however you wish. The name and image is laser engraved on, so there are no toxic paints or dyes to come off. The machine never even touches it. You could easily paint or dye it yourself if you wish. They are left completely natural.

Just let me know the name, a font and a graphic from the collection and I will get it made up for you. I will email a black and white proof so you can double check the spelling before I complete the engraving.

These are not meant to be toys and could pose a choking hazard with small children.

name: personalized pink anodized aluminum mirror
description:
this super slim anodized aluminum mirror can be customized exactly how you'd wish. 

Just let me know your choice of text, font and a graphic

name: small wood buttons branded to your request
description:
you will get 24 awesome buttons for your creations. I have 3/4" or 1" available for this price. They are 1/8" thick and the holes can be exactly to your liking- in size and qty.

these are unpainted and left completely natural.

After purchase I will email you (to the same email you have at paypal) to set up the details. After I get the info, I will send you a photo for approval before I run the whole order.

name: flat wood buttons for branding your products
description:
one set of 24 custom branded buttons with your text or logo.

*1.25" or 1.5" with rounded edges
*completely flat
*holes can be any size and qty you wish - fat for yarn or twine or just large enough for a needle and thread


I will contact you after purchase for the details you need for your button to be created. I make actual samples and send photos before running the whole order.

name: Laser branded leather guitar pick holder - customized
description:
This custom guitar pick holder has a heavy duty snap, two rivets on the side and an eyelet for the chain to go through. It is approx 2" wide and 1 3/4" tall. New it easily holds 5 picks and would hold a lot more as leather loosens up a bit.

This will be customized just for you with a name, your band, monogram or artwork. Great for your key chain or attach to your guitar case. 

Great gift for that awesome rocker of yours!

I have white and brown leather available.

Please ask as many questions as you like! I have a guarantee on the rivets and the snap - you pay postage to me and I'll pay postage back once it is fixed! :) I hate when things break and want this to last a long time!!! leather only looks better with age. Please note the "burned" image may lighten over time as the surface of the leather gets more wear, but is burned in and not painted on - so it will last longer than paint.
